u/pr01/p01_jatekos_nez.asp?p_foverseny=1&p_verseny_id=9603&p_jnkod=268731 Veszpr\u00e9m FC 2012-2013]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Honma, Kazuo}}\n[[Category:1980 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Yokohama]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Thespakusatsu Gunma players]]\n[[Category:FK Ma\u010dva \u0160abac players]]\n[[Category:Tisza Vol\u00e1n SC footballers]]\n[[Category:Lombard-P\u00e1pa TFC footballers]]\n[[Category:Di\u00f3sgy\u0151ri VTK players]]\n[[Category:Ny\u00edregyh\u00e1za Spartacus FC players]]\n[[Category:BFC Si\u00f3fok players]]\n[[Category:Vasas FC players]]\n[[Category:Ferencv\u00e1rosi TC footballers]]\n[[Category:Nemzeti Bajnoks\u00e1g I players]]\n[[Category:Lao Toyota F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Japanese expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Serbia]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Hungary]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Laos]]\n[[Category:Japanese expatriate sportspeople in Serbia]]\n[[Category:Japanese expatriate sportspeople in Hungary]]\n[[Category:Japanese expatriate sportspeople in Laos]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-forward-1980s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2017}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name        = Kazuo Honma\n| image       = Kazuo Honma.jpg\n| image_size  = 250\n| caption     = \n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|1980|3|17|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = [[Yokohama]], [[Kanagawa Prefecture]], [[Japan]]\n| height      = {{height|m=1.75|precision=0}}\n| position    = [[Striker (association football)|Striker]]\n| currentclub = [[Lao Toyota FC]]  \n| clubnumber  = 18\n| youthyears1 = 1994\u20131997 \n| youthclubs1 = Omiya Higashi High School\n| years1  = 1998\u20131999 \n| clubs1  = [[Koshigaya F.C.]]                    \n| caps1   =  ? \n| goals1  =  ?\n| years2  = 2000\u20132001 \n| clubs2  = [[Thespa Kusatsu]]                    \n| caps2   =  ? \n| goals2  =  ?\n| years3  = 2002\u20132004 \n| clubs3  = [