{"title_page": "Kazuki Ito", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Kazuki Ito\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Kazuki Ito\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1987|8|8}}\n|birth_place=[[Chiba Prefecture|Chiba]], Japan\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.78}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub=\n|clubnumber=\n|youthyears1=2006\u20132009|youthclubs1=[[Tokai University]]\n|years1=2010\u20132011|clubs1=[[Arte Takasaki]]|caps1=42|goals1=4\n|years2=2012\u20132014|clubs2=[[YSCC Yokohama]]|caps2=70|goals2=9\n|totalcaps=112|totalgoals=13\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|manageryears1=|managerclubs1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update=\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Kazuki Ito'''|\u4f0a\u85e4 \u548c\u57fa|It\u014d Kazuki|born August 8, 1987}} is a former Japanese [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=11916 J.League Data Site]{{in lang|ja}}</ref>\n\n==Playing career==\nKazuki Ito was played for [[Arte Takasaki]] and [[YSCC Yokohama]] from 2010 to 2014.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player|11916}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ito, Kazuki}}\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Tokai University alumni]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Chiba Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J3 League players]]\n[[Category:Japan Football League players]]\n[[Category:Arte Takasaki players]]\n[[Category:YSCC Yokohama players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-forward-1980s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Kazuki Ito\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Kazuki Ito\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1987|8|8}}\n|birth_place=[[Chiba Prefecture|Chiba]], Japan\n|death_date=\n|death_place=\n|height={{Height|m=1.78}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub=\n|club